    <string name="rules">The goal of the game is to gather points by answering questions correctly.\n\n
        There are two roles, the host and the players, with the host sending the questions and the players answering them.\n\n
        The host first must connect to the players before starting a round and loading a question.
        Then they can send the question by pressing the big button on their screen.
        Afterwards, the players fight for the right to answer by pressing their buzzers.
        After a player is deemed the first to press their buzzer, the host listens for their answer and decides whether it is correct or not.\n\n
        If the answer is correct the player gets a point, otherwise they do not.
        The host may then continue the game by starting a new round</string>
